Worms are parasites that feeds on other living organism, including human, to survive.
Every human has worms in their body, which is commonly gotten from the consumption of contaminated foods/waters.
Once in a while, everyone needs to deworm his or herself, and there are various signs that prove one needs to deworm his/her system, which are listed below.
1. One of the major signs, is sudden weight loss. Once you notice weight loss, this proves that the worm present in your system feeds well on your consumed foods, and also drain all nutrients in your body, which causes lost in weight.
2. When you always feel tired, also known as fatigue, then you need to deworm your body.
3. Another major sign that shows you need to deworm your system is constipation, which leads to irritation in your guts, and also interferes with digestion.
4. When you also feel some frequent abdominal pains and also nausea/vomiting, then you need to deworm your system.
5. When you also feel regular hunger unlike the usual, then you need to deworm your system because the worms feed on the food you eat, thereby causing you frequent hunger.
6. Another major sign that proves you need to deworm your system is diarrhea/dehydration.
7. Another sign is when you are unable to sleep well, also known as Insomnia.
Conclusion: Once you notice any of the above listed signs, visit your doctor.


